    au.csiro.pathling.search
     
  • Class
    Description
    DateMatcher
    Matches elements using range-based comparisons for date search parameters.
    ElementMatcher
    A function that matches a single Column element against a search value.
    ExactStringMatcher
    Matches elements using case-sensitive exact equality for the :exact modifier on string search parameters.
    FhirFieldNames
    Centralized constants for FHIR element field names used in search filters.
    MatcherFactory
    Factory interface for creating search filters for a specific search parameter type.
    NumberMatcher
    Matches elements using FHIR numeric search semantics.
    NumericMatchingSupport
    Utility class for numeric matching logic used by both NumberMatcher and QuantityMatcher.
    QuantityMatcher
    Matches Quantity elements using FHIR quantity search semantics.
    QuantitySearchValue
    Represents a parsed FHIR quantity search value.
    ReferenceMatcher
    Matches the reference field of a FHIR Reference element against a search value.
    SearchFilter
    Builds SparkSQL filter expressions from search parameter values.
    SearchPrefix
    Represents comparison prefixes for ordered search parameters (date, number, quantity).
    SearchPrefix.ParsedValue
    Holds both the extracted prefix and the remaining value portion after prefix removal.
    StringMatcher
    Matches elements using case-insensitive starts-with logic for string search parameters.
    TokenMatcher
    Matches elements using token search semantics for various FHIR types.
    UriMatcher
    Matches URI elements against a search value using one of three modes: exact equality, prefix matching (:below), or inverse prefix matching (:above).
